 Thursday 10th , Friday 11th Saturday 12th August 1916 Veri quiet ; day rather warm , veri littl activ on front out from us . Harvest in full swing around us . Sunday 13.8.16 First Anniversari of the format of the 8th F.Amb . Lectur by Major William to all N.C.Os on disciplin . Pte Howard of B.Sec award the D.C.M. for distinguish conduct on the day of the attack ; Juli 19th . Monday 14.8.16 A B Section left for Estair where they are to go into Billet . Tuesday 15.8.16 King Georg pass through Sailli Surround district to day ; seen by a few of our lad . Rain a good deal dure the day . Good news of great Russian
